data.description: Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Home is conveniently located between Southern Blvd and Forest Hill. Recently renovated kitchen and bathrooms plus beautiful new ceramic floor throughout (no carpets).  Impact windows and doors complete. This move in ready condition makes for a wonderful opportunity whether for a family (3 bed/2 bath) or an investor to rent or airbnb (No HOA).  The extra extra large yard leaves plenty of room for a pool, play yard and a guest house! Also room to extend and add to existing home and still room for that family pool!  The location is perfect to enjoy the growing area of restaurants and shops.  Just minutes to the beach or the airport. Hurry before this gem is gone because it will not last!!
